    q  lub  ^C       stop playing and quit program
    o               toggle OSD : none / seek / seek+timer
    /  oraz *        decrease/increase volume
    m               toggle using master/pcm channel for volume setting
    f               toggle fullscreen (only with -vo sdl)

</verb>

</p>
